snippet.title: Pick Axe Pete! -Odyssey² - Best Platform Video Games of All Time
snippet.description:
Pick Axe Pete! - Odyssey², one of the best platform video games of all time.  You can dig for nuggets by reading, watching, listening and playing the history of the Odyssey 2 game console at my video game history website The Dot Eaters: https://thedoteaters.com/?bitstory=console/odyssey%c2%b2

The original Minecraft! One of the best games for the Odyssey² game console, and one of the best platform video games of all time from the classic era of video games. Made by game designer Ed Averett, and released in 1982 by N.A.P.

Facebook 🕹️ https://www.facebook.com/thedoteaters
Twitter 🕹️  https://twitter.com/doteaters
YouTube 🕹️ https://www.youtube.com/user/Umma6umma
